## Geography & coverage

Describe your region the way you'd brief a new researcher: the towns and
neighborhoods that count as "local", nearby places that do NOT count, and any
landmarks or shorthand names agents should recognize. This entire file is
injected verbatim into every agent's prompt.

Example: Coverage is Example County — primarily Springfield and Shelbyville,
plus the Route 9 corridor. Capital City news only counts when it directly
affects county residents (transit, taxes, utilities).

## Seed sources (optional)

The source-keeper agent imports these into its registry on first run.

- https://www.example-town.gov/news
- https://www.example-library.org/events
- https://www.example-county-paper.com
